> for years now, and still stumble on features and tricks.
> So keep workin' at it, post questions here, etc, and your
> skills will really sharpen.

Yeah, it's easy to miss those little tips in the margin too (I think I need
glasses). Like extruding points off a cylinder to make tree-like branches
or using an object as a path when extruding a two dimensional object like a
primitive disk.   Great stuff :-)

-- Bob

