bandwidth, off-topic discussions and the like, but isn't this more of the same?

People should also realize that this list exists because of the grace of a few 
individuals and one company that isn't doing so well - Unisys.  Should any one 
of those parties decide that the list is too much effort, we could all be out in

the cold.  I'm not saying that change isn't good, but beggers can't be choosers.

So unless someone out there is willing to take charge and implement the news 
group, let's get back to our regularly scheduled program - Imagine.

-Scott
spack@adobe.com

P.S. If you do want to implement the news group, please talk to Dave Wickard 
first!


