>have that many PS fonts to play with, so I always made 'logo' objects in 
>Detail.  What happened?  

I think Imagine started behaving like this when the PC version was made. The 
PC users don't have Amiga bitmap fonts so the dropped support for from 
Imagine but FORGOT to remove the relevant menu item. Postscript fonts are 
better anyway IMHO.

Greetings Joop

